*Poznaje* ga već dugo. (He has known him for a long time.)

On *poznaje* njegov glas. (He recognizes his voice.)

Oni se *poznaju* još od detinjstva. (They have known each other since childhood.)

Ona *poznaje* nju već godinama. (She has known her for years.)

On je *poznao* njegova dela. (He has become familiar with his works.)

Mi *poznajemo* njene planove. (We are aware of her plans.)